@startuml

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FEFECE
skinparam noteBorderColor #888888
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor<<context>>  #E8F4F8
    BackgroundColor<<strategy>> #FFE8CC
    BorderColor #444444
}
hide empty members

title Strategy Pattern - Character & Weapon

interface WeaponBehavior {
    + {abstract} useWeapon() : void
}

abstract class Character <<context>> {
    # weapon : WeaponBehavior
    + fight() : void
    + setWeapon(weapon : WeaponBehavior) : void
}

class King    <<context>> extends Character
class Queen   <<context>> extends Character
class Knight  <<context>> extends Character
class Bishop  <<context>> extends Character

class KnifeBehavior        <<strategy>> implements WeaponBehavior
class AxeBehavior          <<strategy>> implements WeaponBehavior
class SpearBehavior        <<strategy>> implements WeaponBehavior
class BowAndArrowBehavior  <<strategy>> implements WeaponBehavior

Character "1" o-- "1" WeaponBehavior : weapon

note right of Character
  <b>Context</b>
  WeaponBehavior 참조를 가지고
  fight() 호출 시 weapon.useWeapon()으로 위임.
  setWeapon()으로 런타임에 무기 교체 가능.
end note

note right of WeaponBehavior
  <b>Strategy 인터페이스</b>
  모든 무기 동작의 공통 규약.
  Character는 구체 무기를 모르고도 동작.
end note

note bottom of KnifeBehavior
  <b>ConcreteStrategies</b>
  각 무기별 useWeapon() 구현.
  Knife    → 칼로 베기
  Axe      → 도끼로 찍기
  Spear    → 창으로 찌르기
  Bow      → 활로 쏘기
end note

@enduml
/'
